    public class Agent_EASearch
extends Agent_Search
    Search agent based on evolutionary algorithms. Has the following options:
    • -E float minimum error rate (default 0.1)
    • -M int maximal number of generations (default 10)
    • -I int maximal number of evaluated configurations (default 100)
    • -T float Mutation rate (default 0.2)
    • -F float Mutation rate per field in individual (default 0.2)
    • -X float Crossover probability (default 0.5)
    • -P int population size (default 10)
    • -L float The percentage of elite individuals (default 0.1)
    It uses one point crossover and a radnom mutation (it generates new random value for selected variables, the generation depends on the type of the variable).
    Author:
    Martin Pilat
